y, who is trying to kill me. I must slay him before he slays me. I will. Before The Tribunal, I swear this creed: my sword and myself are defenders of my land, we are the masters of my enemy, we are the saviors of my life. So be it, until there is no enemy, but peace.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=draxusmt>Draxus MT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 165<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/13/02 9:14:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4642.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: anyone tried...</span><hr size=1> With my luck I would spend half the fight waiting for a snare proc, then be dead or finished with the mob before the fear proc'ed.  -10 dex, ugh. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6347">Veteran Draxus Diablus</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
